The paper deals with concealing rate information in wireless transmissions using cryptographic techniques, which falls under the information theory (cs.IT) and cryptography (cs.CR) sub-categories. The proposed solution also aims to boost the resiliency against interference, which can be related to the networked systems (cs.NI) and systems and control (cs.SY) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper mentions the modulation schemes used in the proposed solution, which can be related to the multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category.
